## 23.5 Frontend API Client Module

### Module Name

`shared/lib/apiClient`

### Interface

```ts
apiClient.get<T>(path: string, options?: RequestOptions): Promise<T>
apiClient.post<T>(path: string, body?: unknown, options?: RequestOptions): Promise<T>
